[2026-03-18T11:48:46.349Z] [STDOUT] {"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01WkhZxHvqhWGWCbhg8pMCC6","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All done. Here's a summary of the changes:\n\n**Problem**: When a persona was at its concurrency limit, events were permanently marked as `partial` or left as `pending` (retrying every 2s without backoff), silently dropping delivery to throttled subscriptions.\n\n**Changes across 5 files:**\n\n1. **`packages/shared/src/types.ts`** — Added `retryAfter: string | null` and `retryCount: number` to `PersonaEvent` interface.\n\n2. **`packages/orchestrator/src/db/schema.ts`** — Added `retry_after TEXT` and `retry_count INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0` columns to the `persona_events` table. Added migrations for both legacy single-DB and per-tenant databases.\n\n3. **`packages/orchestrator/src/db/events.ts`** — \n   - Updated row mapper with the new fields\n   - Modified `getPendingEvents` query: `WHERE status = 'pending' AND (retry_after IS NULL OR retry_after <= datetime('now'))` so deferred events are skipped until their backoff expires\n   - Added `deferEventForRetry()` — sets `retry_after = now + min(5 * 2^retryCount, 60)s`, increments `retry_count`, keeps status as `pending`\n\n4. **`packages/orchestrator/src/db/index.ts`** — Exported `deferEventForRetry`.\n\n5. **`packages/orchestrator/src/eventProcessor.ts`** — Changed throttle handling:\n   - **All throttled**: calls `deferEventForRetry` with exponential backoff instead of immediately resetting to `pending`\n   - **Some delivered + some throttled**: now defers for retry instead of marking `partial` (dead) — this is the key correctness fix\n   - **Some delivered + some failed (no throttle)**: still marks `partial` (genuine failure, not throttling)\n   - **All failed**: still marks `failed`\n\n**Backoff schedule**: 5s → 10s → 20s → 40s → 60s (capped), ensuring throttled events don't hammer the processor but eventually get delivered when capacity frees up."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":353,"cache_read_input_tokens":64085,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":353},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"43babe3f-d692-4a25-8476-901485a68cf5","uuid":"48d5254c-0ab9-4faa-9c72-dc89a9ba4332"}
